  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Yesterday I voted in favour of new eligibility criteria for free school meals which will mean 50,000 more children will benefit from a free school meal by 2020 when compared to the previous benefits system under Labour.<a href="https://t.co/8Rw0pyyQP3" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/8Rw0pyyQP3</a></p>

The company has had a factory on the same site for over a century and is an example of a British business that has a global outlook; importing sugar cane from all over the world.<a href="https://t.co/8ITn35GKmD" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/8ITn35GKmD</a></p>

        <h2 class="SignupDialog-heading">Not on Twitter? Sign up, tune into the things you care about, and get updates as they happen.</h2>
